msgstr "Število notranjih ravni"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:71
msgid ""
"Partners and children are shown as arcs below the ancestor section. The fan "
"size is limited to 180–270 degrees when enabled."
msgstr ""
"Partnerji in otroci so prikazani kot loki pod razdelkom prednikov. Velikost "
"pahljače je omejena na 180–270 stopinj, ko je omogočeno."

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/colors.phtml:39
